          "name": "First-time login - New user signs up with passkey and lands on home screen which then prompts them to join the root garden",
          "roles": ["Gardener", "Operator"],
          "platform": "Mobile",
          "priority": "P0",
          "status": "Passed",
          "type": "Functional",
          "story": "issues/2",
          "preconditions": [
            "Test environment is up and reachable on mobile (PWA or mobile web)",
            "Passkey / WebAuthn is supported and enabled on the device + browser",
            "Root garden exists in the system and is configured as the default/joinable garden",
            "User is logged out; no existing session or cached auth state in the app"
          ],
          "steps": [
            "Open the Green Goods app on a mobile device (or mobile browser)",
            "On the landing/auth screen, tap Login (or equivalent)",
            "When the OS passkey prompt appears, complete the flow (Face ID / fingerprint / device PIN, etc.)",
            "Wait for the app to finish registration/login and load the authenticated view",
            "Observe the first authenticated screen (home screen)",
            "Observe the prompt to join the root garden (toaster)",
            "(Optional for full flow) Tap Join root garden and confirm any join action"
          ],
          "expected": [
            "A new account is created and linked to the device passkey with no errors",
            "User is redirected to the gardener home screen after successful authentication",
            "There is no intermediate blank/undefined state; a loading indicator is shown while processing",
            "The home screen clearly shows a prompt to join the root garden, with clear CTA text",
            "If the user signs the passkey transaction they are successfully added to that garden and the UI updates"
          ],
          "notes": [
            "Messaging should make it obvious this is a one-time setup and that passkey = secure login, not a social login",
            "The join root garden prompt should explain why this matters",
            "Watch for any jank between auth success and home loading (spinners vs. blank white screen)",
            "Consider a small success microcopy: You're in! Let's connect you to your first garden."
          ]
        },
